Cryptographic features 231 – Can use EC-521 strength migration zones when working with EP11 HSMs  Launch Point For CHIM - For clients that also have IBM 4769 HSMs on linux x86, AIX x86, or Power AIX servers those HSMs can be managed using the Cryptographic Hardware Initialization and Maintenance (CHIM) feature of TKE.  New default wrapping method for the Crypto Express8S HSM.  New AES DUKPT key attribute on AES DKYGENKY parts.  New EP11 attributes and control points can be managed from the TKE.  Smart Card Reader Buzzer – For Identiv smart card readers, the reader's buzzer can be controlled by the TKE.
